==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Micromillimeter
<hw>Mi`cro*mil"li*me`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Micro-</ets> + <ets>millimeter</ets>.]</ety> <def>The
millionth part of a meter.</def> <note>The millionth part of a meter is
now termed a <altname>micron</altname>, and the word
<ex>micromillimeter</ex> does not conform to the IS use of the prefix
<er>micro-</er>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

